Buddy.farm is a unofficial, player-managed companion site to FarmRPG. It is ran by the staff member [user]Coderanger[/user] and has tons and tons of excellent info.

Need to find where to get an item? What to give to townsfolk to get higher levels? Which location has the best droprates? All of that and more are available. Things are being added all the time. Be sure to visit regularly

